Features:
- Session Management
  -> See Fvwm-Crystal
  -> use LxSession?
- Composite Manager for real transparency
  - Cairo -> http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YBbeFCYdHno
  - xcompmgr
- localisation (de -> po files) for manpages, menus, help windows
- own config folder: ~/.fvwm-nightshade
- icons on desktop with idesk (tools: http://icecc.sourceforge.net/idesktools.html)
- own config tool for the most important options (gtk2, perl or python)
- applets -> minimoids (http://box-look.org/content/show.php?content=137027)
  -> must be rewritten to fit into FNS (svgs or use default icons, more configurable, ...)

Documentation:
- F1 help (asciidoc for html & manpage)
- Wiki on Github (also asciidoc) with helps, screenshots, etc
- NEWS, INSTALL, ...

Package Management:
- deb
  -> http://www.debian.org/doc/manuals/maint-guide/index.de.html
  -> http://www.debian.org/doc/manuals/debian-faq/ch-pkg_basics.de.html
- rpm
  -> http://www.linux-community.de/Internal/Artikel/Print-Artikel/LinuxUser/2006/07/RPM-Pakete-selbst-erstellen
- Makefile for make-install/uninstall (tar.gz file for no package installation)
- Suse build service for Repo
  -> http://de.opensuse.org/openSUSE:Build_Service_Anleitung

